title: We Talk to 3 Listeners Who Think They Might Get Engaged Before the Holidays
description: A lot of people get engaged around the holidays so we thought we would see if anyone out there is thinking they'll be getting engaged this month and then check in with them over the next few weeks to see if it happened!
